&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;What we do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At runZero, we&#39;re a team of dreamers and creative thinkers who aren&#39;t afraid to shake up the status quo. Fixing what’s broken with legacy vulnerability management and overcoming persistent, decades-old problems requires a new approach.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our platform provides a single source of truth for exposure management across the total attack surface. Without requiring agents, authentication, or appliances, runZero delivers&amp;nbsp; the most complete and accurate visibility into every asset and exposure across&amp;nbsp; internal, external, IT, OT, IoT, mobile, and cloud environments — including uncovering&amp;nbsp; unknown and unmanageable devices and broad classes of exposures that evade traditional tools.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Founded by HD Moore (creator of Metasploit), runZero is trusted by more than 500 companies and 30,000 users worldwide to find and mitigate risks faster, meet compliance requirements, and improve overall security. See for yourself with a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.runzero.com/try/&quot;&gt;free trial&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Business Development Representative (East),&lt;/strong&gt; you&#39;ll play a pivotal role in driving our revenue growth. Serving as a vital link between marketing and sales, you&#39;ll lead outreach efforts to expand into new markets and qualify warm leads to strengthen our sales pipeline. Your focus will be on research, targeted prospecting, and generating high-quality opportunities that highlight our unique value proposition.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This strategic role gives you the autonomy to be creative/proactive with your outbound and inbound strategies. So you won’t be given a script to repeat. Instead, you’ll be given goals and work with your manager to build the messaging/workflows/strategies needed to achieve them together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop new business opportunities from net-new greenfield accounts that align with runZero’s ICP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find and qualify leads through outbound prospecting methods using our sales automation tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally with multiple stakeholders (account executives, marketing, sales operations, fellow BDRs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee and maintain a pipeline of interested prospects, while strategically partnering with account executives to create and utilize playbooks to win prioritized accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create account plans by conducting research and synthesizing information and other materials that reflect a grasp of runZero’s customers’ needs and how runZero delivers value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write emails and letters you&#39;d love to open; ask compelling questions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help drive target contacts to attend marketing events and reply to our campaigns by following up on Account-Based Marketing campaigns and partnering with Marketing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete accurate tracking of communication with current and potential customers in our CRM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about delighting customers with exceptional relationship-building&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A drive to meet and exceed monthly and quarterly goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Genuine curiosity and excitement about IT security&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An effective listener, with excellent written and verbal communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently and as part of a team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proactive contributor in meetings who consistently expresses thoughtful ideas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
